   Lobstruck walked around in his beast mode. "Geez, boring, no life 
here Lobstruck *yawn* terrorize"  He walked around looking for any 
sign of life on earth. He noticed alot Deer Grazing. He pulled out
his 
doubble barrel pulse shotgun. He fired to pulse at the deer. He saw
as 
many of them run. He looked down and saw he killed three with 2
shots. 
He smiled as he ran down the hill and pulled out the Deer hearts. He 
put it into a little bag that he was caring as he continued looking 
for any bot life in this world. 

   He saw a forest. He entered it as he continued looking some bot.
He 
pulled out his sword as he cut some trees in half. He then looked the 
way he just came. He fired a rocket as he watched the flames start to 
burn down the tree's, "Slag, where is all the bots life on this 
planet." He looked all over for any sign of robot life.
